    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>游戏简介</u></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >驱魔师是一款2D的动作游戏，在各种关卡会出现各式各样的敌人，包括中国僵尸丶日式妖怪和古埃及精灵，打倒敌人後会获得经验及升级，升级後角色的能力会增强，更容易通关。游戏中存在各种谜团及传说中的强敌，你能否解开谜团及战胜他们？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026650/extras/b59dcb4dbc7e6659758586605341371b.avif?t=1765360565\" width=1558 height=754 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026650/extras/50cec168030409ee6c8b45fa36e0a808.avif?t=1765360565\" width=1560 height=674 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026650/extras/72a333323434219269217325a90b1111.avif?t=1765360565\" width=1560 height=812 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026650/extras/4676604e8d9ab7df6d495463b0e00223.avif?t=1765360565\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. 选择角色：可以选择玄华或莉莎，并可在游戏中途切换角色；  <br>2. 地图模式：可在小镇到处逛逛，搜集情报及购买物品；   <br>3. 多层关卡：共有15层关卡；   <br>4. 各种技能：玄华和莉莎拥有不同的技能及能力；   <br>5. 角色升级：打倒敌人会获得经验及升级，升级後可分配升级点数以提升角色的能力；   <br>6. 各种属性：敌人拥有各自的属性，装着有利的装备可以较易获胜；   <br>7. 解开谜团：谜团存在於特定关卡；   <br>8. 隐藏强敌：传说中的强敌隐藏在特定关卡内，战胜他们能获得特别的道具；   <br>9. 多种结局：具有多於一种的结局；   <br>10.困难模式：打倒最终头目後，可选择困难模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>背景</u></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在平静的小镇佛罗伦斯最近发生了各种怪事，被邪灵占领的大屋丶被附身的人丶失踪的孩子丶奇妙的传说等，这些怪事困扰着居民，令众人束手无策，甚至感到绝望。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >刚到此地的玄华及教会的莉莎拥有不可思议的天赋，他们能否凭籍自身的力量解决这些怪事，找到及消除引发怪事的元凶，帮助镇上的居民，令小镇回归平静和快乐？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了认证目的，运行此游戏需要： <br>1. 互联网连线；  <br>2. 运行Steam客户端；  <br>3. 在Steam客户端登入Steam用户帐号。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>操作说明</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026650/extras/246742e9f980c1416a853437345411b9.avif?t=1765360565\" width=173 height=292 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>若拟使用控制器</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >方法一：使用预设的控制器设定 &quot;The Exorcists 20251020&quot;。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026650/extras/5ab49cc6eb9db3a1b825e4f4b6f84ac4.avif?t=1765360565\" width=1560 height=1857 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >方法二：自行设定控制器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026650/extras/8d8f6f86720139450beec982676edb28.avif?t=1765360565\" width=1560 height=552 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026650/extras/b27cb8b6f8148749b1a2c70ba38740cf.avif?t=1765360565\" width=1560 height=468 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >接着，请对按键进行设定。我所使用的是通用（DirectInput）控制器，下图为我的控制器之设定，仅供参考。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026650/extras/886c230e683ffa62c2c995951bae706c.avif?t=1765360565\" width=1560 height=798 /></span></p>",
